reviewText: If your life is taking a turn for the worse, it may be time for you to be "born again." By watching New ID and following its simple directions, you can start over with a clean slate and cover up past credit, employment, health, marital or legal problems. Discover how to travel overseas more safely without your U.S. passport. See how to protect professional and financial secrets through alternate ID. Learn how to "drop dead" and resurface with a new past and future; get a new valid driver's license, birth certificate and Social Security number; leave dead-end clues to divert your pursuers; and start life over!
